{"tid":960762,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"認真 我覺得手機Game係取代唔到電腦Game","createTime":"2018-12-29T16:16:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T16:37:10.000Z","uid":10277,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f84ed458ca59763a1eca838e5b883bb75d8e6168","tid":960762,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:16:23.000Z","msg":"就好像傳說對決同英雄聯盟咁，<br />\n有啲嘢，<br />\n就是誰都取代不了。<br />\n<br />\n話說，<br />\n朋友以前很喜歡玩永恆冒險，<br />\n出了手機版，<br />\n他玩了玩，<br />\n他說 「不是以前那種感覺。」<br />\n<br />\n聽說，<br />\n我以前最愛的遊戲&mdash;跑Online，<br />\n會出手機版，<br />\n我說 「不了，<br />\n手機到底要如何DJ呢？」<br />\n<br />\n手機遊戲操作簡單化，目的只是想賣人設，求課金。<br />\n<br />\n電腦Online Game的沒落，是科技世代的淘汰，<br />\n也是遊戲生產商的不爭氣，以前熱門的遊戲，<br />\n十居八九都是從韓國遊戲商代理過來，<br />\n現在玩的手機遊戲，許多都是從電腦移植過來，<br />\n搬了身軀卻沒能搬走神韻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呻下，想玩拿拿臨Online姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9297b743848a2ea70aa3749c03a037b2f10b25","tid":960762,"uid":164092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:23:12.000Z","msg":"Steam死咗先開Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c5c96403a57aea15b95711554736b87095c4a7a","tid":960762,"uid":47529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:23:21.000Z","msg":"想玩唔係黑橘代理既瑪奇"},{"pid":"2c68691997608ae35bb700dc92ae076954ab7e58","tid":960762,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d9297b743848a2ea70aa3749c03a037b2f10b25","tid":960762,"uid":164092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:23:12.000Z","msg":"Steam死咗先開Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:24:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Dolly"},{"pid":"021d1a8216d0ff4030b37897f06d